snippet.title: Starfield – Official Announcement Teaser
snippet.description: Discover Starfield, the new space epic currently in development by Bethesda Game Studios. Starfield is the first new franchise in twenty-five years from the acclaimed developers of The Elder Scrolls and Fallout series. Learn more at https://beth.games/2JPSZRc
